Lightweight, narc-free image/video/audio gallery software -- host your own!

Based on FuckFlickr: http://fffff.at/fuckflickr-info

-- WARNING: alpha-stage software -- under active development -- 

__________________________________________________________________________

Installation
  1. Unzip and upload the “fat-media” directory to your server.
  2. Put audio, video, and images or folders into the /data subdirectory.
  3. Visit yourdomain.com/fat-media — the first visit will 
     generate thumbnails!

Bonus:
  4. After the first visit, download and open a folder's info.yml to edit
     titles & descriptions.
  5. Customize config.php to your liking and create/edit your theme.


